title: Zoo Walkthrough 1 — Arrival
story: friendly-zoo
description: Chained full-playthrough, chapter 1 of 5. Entrance pickups (map, brochure, keycard), the first closing announcement at turn 5, and the walk to the Main Path. Run the wt chain with --chain; state persists into wt-02.
---

# --- Zoo Entrance: opening room + contents list ---
> look
[OK: contains "Zoo Entrance"]
[OK: contains "Willowbrook"]
[OK: contains "staff keycard"]

# Identity description through the phrase path
> examine yourself
[OK: contains "visitor"]

# Souvenir map: taking awards `collected` via the after-taking clause
# (interceptor postExecute — the zoo-chain stdlib fix, 2026-07-12).
> take map
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Readable with implicit take; awards `read`
> read brochure
[OK: contains "first taking the zoo brochure"]
[OK: contains "WILLOWBROOK FAMILY ZOO"]
[OK: contains "EXHIBITS"]

# Turn 5: the PA timeline's first closing announcement rides this turn.
> take keycard
[OK: contains "Taken"]
[OK: contains "closing in three hours"]

> south
[OK: contains "Main Path"]
[OK: contains "zookeeper"]
